   <p><strong>Importance:</strong>&nbsp;According to Stewart<strong>&nbsp;</strong>".... most modern technology, from electric lighting to digital cameras could not have been invented without them." Imaginary numbers allow for complex analysis, which allows engineers to solve practical problems working in the plane.</p>
